## FinanceBot environment variables (copy to .env, fill in real values)

## Postgres
POSTGRES_DB=financebot
POSTGRES_USER=financebot
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=change-me

## Connection string for the bot (uses the docker-compose Postgres service)
ConnectionStrings__Default=Host=postgres;Port=5432;Database=financebot;Username=financebot;Password=change-me

## Telegram bot token (from @BotFather)
Telegram__BotToken=

## Anthropic Claude API key
Claude__ApiKey=

## First admin telegram id (numeric). Add more as Auth__AdminUserIds__1, __2, ...
Auth__AdminUserIds__0=

## Telegram delivery mode: Polling | Webhook
Telegram__Mode=Polling

## Cluster discovery method: config | dns | kubernetes-api
Akka__Discovery__Method=config

## Akka cluster seed (single-node default = self)
Akka__Cluster__SeedNodes__0=akka.tcp://financebot@localhost:4053

## Logging
Logging__LogLevel__Default=Information
Logging__LogLevel__Akka=Warning
